articles.title: India successfully test-fires Agni-5 ballistic missile from Odisha
articles.description: India successfully test-fired Agni-5 ballistic missile from Odisha [1, 3].

articles.title: Israeli strikes hit Yemeni capital Sanaa
articles.description: Israeli strikes hit Yemeni capital Sanaa, targeting areas near the Presidential complex and missile bases, following a missile fired towards Israel by Houthi militants two days prior [3].

articles.title: Zelenskyy: Ukraine does not consult with US over long-range missile strikes
articles.description: Ukraine's PM discusses security guarantees with Trump envoy in Kyiv [2]. Zelenskyy stated that Ukraine does not consult with the US over long-range missile strikes [2].
